# Responsive Login Page

A simple responsive login form built with **HTML & CSS**.

## Features
- Responsive design
- Centered login card
- Clean styling with hover effects
- Beginner-friendly project

## Live Demo
https://davidokoni09.github.io/responsive-login-page/

## 🛠️ Built With
- HTML5
- CSS3

## 📚 Lessons Learned
While building this project, I practiced:
- Using semantic HTML form elements
- Basic CSS layout (Grid & Flexbox)
- Styling buttons and input fields
